{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">了解离子反应发生的条件。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Na<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub>&nbsp;+ 2HCl = 2NaCl + H<sub>2</sub>O + CO<sub>2</sub>&uarr;</span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：试管。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：碳酸钠溶液、稀盐酸。</span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">在试管中加入2ml碳酸钠溶液，然后加入2ml稀盐酸，观察实验现象。</span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">有气泡产生。</span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}